hopobject.body: Can I take your number? superbeets neogenis Android: the Nexus 7, for all its various pros, still has the con of being an Android device. This means you have lower quality apps available than the iPad across the board, and many of the most popular apps end up arriving on Android six months to a year late. Android devices are also more crash prone thanks to the way in which apps are allowed to misbehave in the background, and more susceptible to malware. For all the “openness” which Android fans brag about, that openness often translates to chaos which gets in the way of the user experience.
